Register a RL policy with {p}`name`.

```
param name

Key with which the policy will be registered.
If  will use the name of the class
```

```py
from habitat_baselines.rl.ppo.policy import Policy
from habitat_baselines.common.baseline_registry import (
    baseline_registry
)

@baseline_registry.register_policy
class MyPolicy(Policy):
    pass


# or

@baseline_registry.register_policy(name="MyPolicyName")
class MyPolicy(Policy):
    pass
```

Register a Observation Transformer with {p}`name`.

```
param name

